platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Prt--Template helps fashion designers quickly transform a look from concept to runway. The app provides figure templates with front, side, and rear views, along with the basic outline for various items of clothing that you can sketch over. The app is optimized for Apple Pencil, sensing how much pressure you apply with each stroke so you can give your designs just the right texture and intensity of color.
Quickly transform a look from concept to catwalk with this app for fashion designers. Optimised for Apple Pencil, it will let you give your designs just the right texture and intensity of colour.
